Title: Login Verification

Feature: As a user, I want to be able to login with the correct credentials to my account, so that I can verify that my login is successful

Acceptance criteria

Upon successful login, I should be directed to the homepage and see the page title contains “QA Interview Test | DLG Digital"”


Scenario: Login Verification

Given: I am on chrome browser and navigate to the login page "https://login.dev.qa-experience.com"
When:  I enter Username as "test@qa-experience.com"
And:   I enter password as “Password1”
Then:  Login should pass
And:   I should be directed to the Home-Page
And:   I should see title of page which contains "QA Interview Test | DLG Digital"
